flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Start of a new production run or changeover event.]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Retrieve production specifications from SAP S/4HANA.]
  N1 --> N2[Agent: Agentic AI - Plan and execute press setup and tooling installation.]
  N2 --> N3{Agent: Agentic AI - Perform first-piece inspection and approve results.}
  N3 -->|Primary| N4[Agent: Agentic AI - Configure stamping production run based on optimized settings.]
  N4 --> N5[Agent: Agentic AI - Continuously monitor and adjust in-process quality.]
  N5 --> N6[Agent: Agentic AI - Collect and report production metrics.]
  N6 --> N7[Agent: Agentic AI - Handle and package parts post-stamping.]
  N7 --> Z1[Outcome: Minimized COGS, reduced changeovers, prevented defects, improved OTIF, and optimized overall production efficiency.]
  N3 -->|First-piece inspection fails.| B1[Reconfigure press setup and retry inspection.]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Ensure initial stamped parts meet specifications.]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Quality adjustments exceed tolerance ...| B2[Halt production and investigate root cause.]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Prevent defective parts from entering production.]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N3 -->|Post-stamping handling instructions a...| B3[Generate default handling instructions.]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Ensure proper part handling and packaging.]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]